decision_conditions:
Condition : 12 - A Landscape Management Plan, including management responsibilities and maintenance schedules for all hard and soft landscaped areas on the site shall be submitted to and approved in writing prior to the occupation of the development. The Landscape Management Plan shall be carried out as approved for the lifetime of the development.  The Landscape Management Plan shall cover all of the landscaped areas, and in relation to the linear park shall include the following details: 

(a)	monthly and annual maintenance of the Linear Park including provision for: 

(i)	procedures and arrangements for the maintenance of all bushes, trees, shrubs and grasslands and the replacement of damaged or dead trees, shrubs and bushes; 

(ii)	procedures and arrangements for the adequate repair, maintenance and cleaning of the facilities; 

(iii)	procedures and arrangements for the adequate collection and disposal of all litter, debris and wastes.
